>\n食唔死人既<br />\n利申：試過 叫左個得紫菜既烏東</blockquote><br />\n通常睇到隔離食乜就叫乜<br />\n無人既就鳩叫, 講真好少中伏...."},{"pid":"93002c7f1932495e2a0c3acbfcc4174ed26c3081","tid":288084,"uid":44828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T03:24:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>偏遠少少英文已經唔太得<br />\n不過好多入面都有少少漢字, 基本上都估到<br />\n真係唔知既咪google translate囉, 大概意思都會明既</blockquote><br />\n傳言日本人英文極差<br />\n有咩事好似會好無助咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有d真係好差，第一次去買野同個女仔雞同鴨講 <br />\n佢拎部電話出黎即時翻譯返 原來係叫我等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7252104d67520a1fa42a03425dd005795a000db","tid":288084,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T03:24:28.000Z","msg":"睇你去邊 去名勝唔洗 其他深度遊要"},{"pid":"9ea22b995581f7c6dc9a0cf5ad8c9766231982ae","tid":288084,"uid":79979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T03:25:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>反而我覺得偏遠啲嘅地方有多啲漢字睇<br />\n舊啲嘅地方反而無用咁多平假</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似2月份去四國+小豆島<br />\n門票佢哋唔係用チケット<br />\n而係用舊式既きっぷ/ 或者漢字切符<br />\n之前學日文聲些話呢個字好少人用，好舊<br />\n一出到神戶大阪就見返チケット<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"867632faba5873f81b0ecc2a9f4bbc6b62744d70","tid":288084,"uid":53261,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T03:25:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>偏遠少少英文已經唔太得<br />\n不過好多入面都有少少漢字, 基本上都估到<br />\n真係唔知既咪google translate囉, 大概意思都會明既</blockquote><br />\n傳言日本人英文極差<br />\n有咩事好似會好無助咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有d真係好差，第一次去買野同個女仔雞同鴨講 <br />\n佢拎部電話出黎即時翻譯返 原來係叫我等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你真係連基本日文都唔識<br />\n<br />\n去返英語系國家啦"},{"pid":"e23747f2b9f42fe6d058b739ea96dff606804aa6","tid":288084,"uid":70817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T03:26:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>偏遠少少英文已經唔太得<br />\n不過好多入面都有少少漢字, 基本上都估到<br />\n真係唔知既咪google translate囉, 大概意思都會明既</blockquote><br />\n傳言日本人英文極差<br />\n有咩事好似會好無助咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你開個google translate 譯你想講既單詞日文俾佢就得 <br />\n餐廳你用google translate影相譯都夠晒啦<br />\n有線索點都鳩估到食咩既"},{"pid":"f444bcfb68d888b4e5ab33d7c4c1c631284f5e38","tid":288084,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T03:26:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>偏遠少少英文已經唔太得<br />\n不過好多入面都有少少漢字, 基本上都估到<br />\n真係唔知既咪google translate囉, 大概意思都會明既</blockquote><br />\n傳言日本人英文極差<br />\n有咩事好似會好無助咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一離開左遊客區就係咁, 不過呢d經驗的感受黎<br />\n講真可以有咩事丫, 黎黎去去咪又係盪失路整親跌錢跌passport<br />\n好多好肯幫你, 就算雞同鴨講都好, 都儘量指俾你睇<br />\n有部上到網既ipad跟身會好好多"},{"pid":"848054289bbb1e355764e62d74388778e5f0f349","tid":288084,"uid":79979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T03:28:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>要,,去餐廳全日字又冇圖。（好食/高級個d)</blockquote><br />\n就係講緊le d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成份野都唔知寫乜實好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇價錢 鳩叫就得<br />\n食唔死人既<br />\n利申：試過 叫左個得紫菜既烏東</blockquote><br />\n通常睇到隔離食乜就叫乜<br />\n無人既就鳩叫, 講真好少中伏....</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果識日文又有外語拼音底子，去舊式喫茶店食嘢，menu會好易睇<br />\n因為大部分都係片假名，照拼個音就知係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4899a3c7522d70b3ffb547b4f3963c407b678cc6","tid":288084,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T03:30:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>偏遠少少英文已經唔太得<br />\n不過好多入面都有少少漢字, 基本上都估到<br />\n真係唔知既咪google translate囉, 大概意思都會明既</blockquote><br />\n傳言日本人英文極差<br />\n有咩事好似會好無助咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有d真係好差，第一次去買野同個女仔雞同鴨講 <br />\n佢拎部電話出黎即時翻譯返 原來係叫我等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n日本人雖然有學英文<br />\n如果土炮其實佢地學英文都幾大問題 因為有D音發唔到 你會覺得佢地好差 同埋佢地好多野唔洗用英文加上地方名會用日文音做併音 唔似香港 中瑻叫CENTRAL呢D意譯 <br />\n日本人做你生意耐性唔錯 HELPFUL 當然 文化同佢地一工難求有關 點都低聲下氣同你認低威 香港人得寸進尺唔好成日表現畀人睇啦 <br />\n日本好多和食屋都好好味 我同女友唔會揀D書仔講既 話晒我聽同睇都OK 講差D 女友直情識聽講睇 <br />\n<br />\n好多大陸留學生 香港女人嫁過去 基本上 遊客區無難度 <br />\n<br />\n大丈夫!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"1667d8ae782c8168fa453c6c1912a0525b50e75f","tid":288084,"uid":44828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T03:30:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>偏遠少少英文已經唔太得<br />\n不過好多入面都有少少漢字, 基本上都估到<br />\n真係唔知既咪google translate囉, 大概意思都會明既</blockquote><br />\n傳言日本人英文極差<br />\n有咩事好似會好無助咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有d真係好差，第一次去買野同個女仔雞同鴨講 <br />\n佢拎部電話出黎即時翻譯返 原來係叫我等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你真係連基本日文都唔識<br />\n<br />\n去返英語系國家啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家學緊日文 再隔一年先再去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"251ed0e55b6cb4b9695f3851a657b3ddea474b7e","tid":288084,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T03:30:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>要,,去餐廳全日字又冇圖。（好食/高級個d)</blockquote><br />\n就係講緊le d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成份野都唔知寫乜實好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇價錢 鳩叫就得<br />\n食唔死人既<br />\n利申：試過 叫左個得紫菜既烏東</blockquote><br />\n通常睇到隔離食乜就叫乜<br />\n無人既就鳩叫, 講真好少中伏....</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果識日文又有外語拼音底子，去舊式喫茶店食嘢，menu會好易睇<br />\n因為大部分都係片假名，照拼個音就知係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以咁講 不過就算串到個音都未必知係乜"},{"pid":"421210394bad37ac0970c7979181d028b48be97e","tid":288084,"uid":33917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T03:32:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>これこれこれ ありがとうございました</blockquote><br />\n直接this this this thank you咪算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08dce702a1029499d09239cf6a9cfac68f6d1cdf","tid":288084,"uid":59140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T03:33:39.000Z","msg":"唔識五十音<br />\n點都要識講arigatou sumemasen oregaishimarts<br />\n一至一萬嘅日文 數字 時間 方向<br />\n撘車 去目的地 俾錢 睇時間 成段trip最有用"},{"pid":"0edaec2f46ab49a8bcebb57daaf86ec482805b63","tid":288084,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T03:34:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>これこれこれ ありがとうございました</blockquote><br />\n直接this this this thank you咪算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去GOOGLE 搵 貴店拿手小菜係乜 要一份 多數好食 因為試過<br />\n學小小 句子 應該唔錯"},{"pid":"89abf4e6027fe745bda124aeeee7dba0948328f4","tid":288084,"uid":59140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T03:36:27.000Z","msg":"大部分外來語都用片假名 而外來語都幾普遍<br />\n所以學識片假名就已經贏一半<br />\n<br />\n利申：背極背唔熟五十音"},{"pid":"735a8a5ccd41af58d940918f1774f73e4035173d","tid":288084,"uid":44828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T03:36:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>偏遠少少英文已經唔太得<br />\n不過好多入面都有少少漢字, 基本上都估到<br />\n真係唔知既咪google translate囉, 大概意思都會明既</blockquote><br />\n傳言日本人英文極差<br />\n有咩事好似會好無助咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有d真係好差，第一次去買野同個女仔雞同鴨講 <br />\n佢拎部電話出黎即時翻譯返 原來係叫我等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n日本人雖然有學英文<br />\n如果土炮其實佢地學英文都幾大問題 因為有D音發唔到 你會覺得佢地好差 同埋佢地好多野唔洗用英文加上地方名會用日文音做併音 唔似香港 中瑻叫CENTRAL呢D意譯 <br />\n日本人做你生意耐性唔錯 HELPFUL 當然 文化同佢地一工難求有關 點都低聲下氣同你認低威 香港人得寸進尺唔好成日表現畀人睇啦 <br />\n日本好多和食屋都好好味 我同女友唔會揀D書仔講既 話晒我聽同睇都OK 講差D 女友直情識聽講睇 <br />\n<br />\n好多大陸留學生 香港女人嫁過去 基本上 遊客區無難度 <br />\n<br />\n大丈夫!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n遊客區 好多大鋪入面職員識講中文 好似ドンキ呢D咁，仲埋好多留學生去打工 基本上無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a510e6810ee81987d67e0033c8b24cf93f328768","tid":288084,"uid":29213,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T03:38:13.000Z","msg":"我一句日文都唔識<br />\n但呢三年去左5/6次日本<br />\n都冇問題<br />\n不過主要去大城市<br />\n黎緊想去四國 鹿兒島 較為冇咁熱門既城市都冇諗住學"},{"pid":"1ee198aaddc46ae4b98f0173c81e2fc85fa89a61","tid":288084,"uid":7355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T03:41:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大部分外來語都用片假名 而外來語都幾普遍<br />\n所以學識片假名就已經贏一半<br />\n<br />\n利申：背極背唔熟五十音</blockquote><br />\n我記晒五十音但唔識記片假名"},{"pid":"8f43fa1b419c17a765c2aeac6fd3c5a7baa6778e","tid":288084,"uid":7355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T03:42:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大部分外來語都用片假名 而外來語都幾普遍<br />\n所以學識片假名就已經贏一半<br />\n<br />\n利申：背極背唔熟五十音</blockquote><br />\n我記晒平假名但唔識記片假名</blockquote>"},{"pid":"c62196a25f15eb11b267fa5eca104e9afa5e0d0a","tid":288084,"uid":106368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T03:43:42.000Z","msg":"之前自己去/同朋友去都係冇人識講<br />\n學幾句&quot;邊度？&quot; &quot;幾錢？&quot; 果啲基本就ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然問人之前用日文講句唔好意思，之後講埋唔該就最好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一開始試過用英文溝通，佢哋好似明明地咁答翻我，但係我聽唔明佢講嘅英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"272ac0899305e62714f0034b9cf0a93ddb45ec4d","tid":288084,"uid":87833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T03:44:57.000Z","msg":"洗撚咩， 第一次帶屋企人的去路都沒問過一次"},{"pid":"e4e425464f46a4eee9ef049d7d63f90c608cf105","tid":288084,"uid":16552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T03:48:54.000Z","msg":"識少少好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除非你去d大城市啦, 做旅客生意果d鋪頭咪英文ok囉,<br />\n但想本地d, 有風味d就一定要識少少日文<br />\n識左五十音既平假名片假名, <br />\n加埋d漢字就照打埋去google translate<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ff96717bd88ee7847da1e1e9481e963297790a0","tid":288084,"uid":101550,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T03:49:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>偏遠少少英文已經唔太得<br />\n不過好多入面都有少少漢字, 基本上都估到<br />\n真係唔知既咪google translate囉, 大概意思都會明既</blockquote><br />\n傳言日本人英文極差<br />\n有咩事好似會好無助咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有d真係好差，第一次去買野同個女仔雞同鴨講 <br />\n佢拎部電話出黎即時翻譯返 原來係叫我等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你真係連基本日文都唔識<br />\n<br />\n去返英語系國家啦</blockquote><br />\n要識果種語言先可以去果個國家<br />\n咁九成人都唔洗去旅行啦<br />\n我覺得最緊要係守規舉唔好搞事<br />\n有乜唔識咪google下<br />\n利申一句日文都唔識一樣玩得好開心"},{"pid":"ef0c7c477e42a64b4e8777f0a35a4960f3a6ae17","tid":288084,"uid":44828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T03:51:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前自己去/同朋友去都係冇人識講<br />\n學幾句&quot;邊度？&quot; &quot;幾錢？&quot; 果啲基本就ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然問人之前用日文講句唔好意思，之後講埋唔該就最好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一開始試過用英文溝通，佢哋好似明明地咁答翻我，但係我聽唔明佢講嘅英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上次搵唔間民宿，有個宅急便大叔唔識英文但係好有耐性咁教我地點去 用好慢既日文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，好彩岩岩學識左右轉彎直行<br />\n最尾平安到達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好好人 佢仲要派緊件 見我地好無奈 主動走黎問我地係唔係旅客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好感動"},{"pid":"410a53e8ae1835b1c708e7c11738f28bd02aba3d","tid":288084,"uid":4242,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T03:51:12.000Z","msg":"唔好話日文/英文.<br />\n去日本唔駛識講野都得."},{"pid":"118386875f5e8f110977859958541e74a38f0216","tid":288084,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T03:55:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6b91a8860cb490a423cf55d1061d3cc7afffeefb","tid":288084,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T03:57:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對日本唔太認識<br />\n日文知識可以話零<br />\n<br />\n獨遊情況下<br />\n淨係用英文問路睇地圖有冇可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n緊係要識啦，上次唔識去到七日都冇野落肚，因為唔識叫佢地唔識聽，車又搭唔到要行路返機場，唔識真係唔好去。"},{"pid":"8a16180188b25f88177f48ef5dc614bb387bbd68","tid":288084,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T03:58:10.000Z","msg":"年中咁撚多人去日本，個個都識日文呀on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6110e28de1e1454d57b2e55926a2acd6f4b3d7f8","tid":288084,"uid":117786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T03:58:47.000Z","msg":"唔學番一兩年日文課程都唔好去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08c42d28dac29f14567f858b78bb2a32227b9465","tid":288084,"uid":374,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T04:00:49.000Z","msg":"唔識當然冇問題<br />\n但識左日文你去旅行嘅歡樂會多好多"},{"pid":"6fcd24d72d939830c87ab4977ce79bf252cea14e","tid":288084,"uid":16480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T04:00:52.000Z","msg":"去旅行 學返幾句當地語言都冇壞既"},{"pid":"7c170cff29bfe87c623f58c9ec0cacaef968ab56","tid":288084,"uid":105428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T04:01:50.000Z","msg":"東京用英文都可以<br />\n唔太難<br />\n幾有趣"},{"pid":"3ad465ac73cf32218337140de1305b25814f405b","tid":288084,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T04:53:56.000Z","msg":"去幾日就唔洗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77c71990e6cc65f3e2136d676f30eedae78d06a8","tid":288084,"uid":106368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T07:55:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>之前自己去/同朋友去都係冇人識講<br />\n學幾句&quot;邊度？&quot; &quot;幾錢？&quot; 果啲基本就ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然問人之前用日文講句唔好意思，之後講埋唔該就最好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一開始試過用英文溝通，佢哋好似明明地咁答翻我，但係我聽唔明佢講嘅英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上次搵唔間民宿，有個宅急便大叔唔識英文但係好有耐性咁教我地點去 用好慢既日文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，好彩岩岩學識左右轉彎直行<br />\n最尾平安到達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好好人 佢仲要派緊件 見我地好無奈 主動走黎問我地係唔係旅客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好感動</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無論係真定係扮<br />\n日本人真係普遍好有禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"941863f3f009ba2c8edf51cd8146cbb3dcd742e9","tid":288084,"uid":88301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T08:01:36.000Z","msg":"舊年八月自己獨遊東京七日，對日文零認識，都無穿無爛翻到香港<br />\n上個月去東京 越後湯澤 京都 大阪，夾埋三星期，都無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c23242aeb84f4027e9361eef30c4cec54229aa1a","tid":288084,"uid":34468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T08:04:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔識當然冇問題<br />\n但識左日文你去旅行嘅歡樂會多好多</blockquote><br />\n識睇會好好多, 起碼D景點介紹, 搭車, 買野之類會睇得明<br />\n同埋識中文睇漢字本身已經比較容易明日文"},{"pid":"6b05a11907c192c48c16db89a3cd39e5802d9671","tid":288084,"uid":8308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T08:16:56.000Z","msg":"大路地方，有睇過下資料，有google map<br />\n劃定晒車飛，訂好酒店<br />\n<br />\n真係唔覺好需要講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n去幾日冇出過聲都冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a9aed2e22ed8ca7d1a1f11d5183e2bd3ede05fa","tid":288084,"uid":51250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T08:16:59.000Z","msg":"鬼唔知識當地語言會睇到多啲，聽到多啲，但唔識一樣可以照去，唔識就唔去咁你好多地方都唔洗去。<br />\n<br />\n去韓國要識韓文，去法國要識法文，去日本要識日文，去俄國要識俄文，去意大利要識意文。"},{"pid":"fe435e26a4d43c829136c339085d96f5147bd936","tid":288084,"uid":55732,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T08:48:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鬼佬唔識漢字又唔識日文 咪又係咁去日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以成日最叻去 to-ki-o, ki-yo-to, o-sa-ka，Ka-ma-ku-ra 同埋 hi-ro-shi-ma 囉<br />\n<br />\n頂多搭個Himeji，Nara同Takayama"},{"pid":"28da3b3198fb191c0809674b00b41592e2db9a8d","tid":288084,"uid":15302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T08:51:45.000Z","msg":"唔識日文準備去一年日本"},{"pid":"e64506f285fabf66a4da54209a9b74b691d796a1","tid":288084,"uid":40198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T08:58:53.000Z","msg":"SayHi 的 語音翻譯 - SayHi Translate<br />\n<a href=\"https://appsto.re/hk/uojgA.i\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappsto.re%2Fhk%2FuojgA.i&d=bKG2wQMy%2F7tb%2FSDZ1jS93AhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=4162530d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://appsto.re/hk/uojgA.i</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個幾好用！"},{"pid":"fe198e03da670ce86dcbeb663e43014f79639b1c","tid":288084,"uid":5921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T09:03:28.000Z","msg":"驚乜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n身體語言都夠"},{"pid":"3c72fffc8c1790037cad98199ab633e364332d48","tid":288084,"uid":411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T09:05:32.000Z","msg":"上年自己去完大阪京都一星期，唔識日文，淨識英文，冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf0861f16803c11aa5865bf6008054fc5b687bcc","tid":288084,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T09:09:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>驚乜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n身體語言都夠</blockquote><br />\n岩啊，用肢體語言己經搞掂60%情況，再用埋d app <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c63c2cedf42517ac77047e88d22ed58dc05f0479","tid":288084,"uid":95857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T09:11:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>これこれこれ ありがとうございました</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nThis, this and this. Thank you. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7567d4c9b535ba79ab9071311855af9aefde2dcb","tid":288084,"uid":20204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T09:12:22.000Z","msg":"唔識唔好去"},{"pid":"14ac97aaf32c21d785f4fe5782ab275de63432c1","tid":288084,"uid":38609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T09:15:41.000Z","msg":"去旅行都係鍾意個個地方先去既姐<br />\n識返一兩個單詞 一兩句片語<br />\n識得用人地既語言去多謝人已經比到人有好印象啦<br />\n<br />\n去遊客區基本上唔洗識日文<br />\n但係唔好期求人地英文水平好好<br />\n或者用普通話問都得<br />\n但係我去旅行堅持唔會講蝗語"},{"pid":"711692b039d205099bf5c90a123e0026b33719a6","tid":288084,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T09:20:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>鬼佬唔識漢字又唔識日文 咪又係咁去日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以成日最叻去 to-ki-o, ki-yo-to, o-sa-ka，Ka-ma-ku-ra 同埋 hi-ro-shi-ma 囉<br />\n<br />\n頂多搭個Himeji，Nara同Takayama</blockquote><br />\nLol k"},{"pid":"4a8400cfd3dc1ddf5837b823cab0622476275d92","tid":288084,"uid":15851,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T09:28:57.000Z","msg":"崇日撚最鐘意同人講冇N幾N幾唔好去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知洗唔洗奶埋日本人地腳趾呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c9c0f828c7cb8d121261e7f4cb191a1a901640","tid":288084,"uid":29351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T09:40:43.000Z","msg":"唔識當然去無問題 我係去左幾次再下定決心學日文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8a76b31f6df536432da72341ba1b8eefc29d2de","tid":288084,"uid":82629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T09:48:01.000Z","msg":"買枝翻譯筆乜都搞掂啦"},{"pid":"a113a34ddc18e3ad22f7185468b54ce684de4dfd","tid":288084,"uid":72827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T09:54:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成街都講緊普通話</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n只係因為你去d 大路地方"},{"pid":"39907a86f8c690491aa8792f2aca054adabee701","tid":288084,"uid":27718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T10:11:27.000Z","msg":"no<br />\n去俄羅斯都唔洗識俄文啦"},{"pid":"b899fded960ce4e409e3de6496c844a110a1a46b","tid":288084,"uid":113116,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T10:18:34.000Z","msg":"經驗分享，唔洗識。雖然我有基礎日文水平，但唔算必須的<br />\n你平時無啦啦唔會要講野， 我都試過問路，學句唔好意思（su 咪媽些）得架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後指你想去果個地方（電話/圖）佢地睇，佢地都會明你想問路，識去可能會直頭好人到叫你跟住佢，唔識會幫你google,都唔識講返句阿li吉多（多謝/唔該）就問下一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n遊客區d鋪（由其藥妝店）就好多人識英文/普通話<br />\n住hostel d reception通常都識英文<br />\n係食野有時煩d, 遊客區食野一般menu有英文甚至中文字，無既話有d鋪會有份專for外國人menu,<br />\n但非遊客區果d食肆就可能全日文， 你咪唔好揀果d鋪食囉， 不過我覺得唔明d字亂點d野食都幾刺激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n題外話，食快餐店有自助點餐機果d提你先，係入左錢先click食咩既， 我之前第一次去咩都唔識以為揀左食咩先最後入錢，部機狂響句日文，響勁多次，我唔知咩事，有個食緊既日本人直頭望住我就嚟由個位起身去幫我，我先醒覺，係要入左錢先揀（響果句日文依家知係話唔夠錢，好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n再嚟搭車就dl返個乘換按內app,基本上都係睇app搭車，唔洗講野，搭多幾次車就慣點睇架喇<br />\n所以其實唔洗識日文，學句su咪媽些（唔好意思）同阿li吉多（多謝）夠架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68acf833e99929b9113e0bcbda4d003b88eb3b26","tid":288084,"uid":66202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T10:55:47.000Z","msg":"帶部手機買張data sim/ wifi蛋, 地圖翻譯google幫你搞掂晒, 天氣交通營業時間旅遊資訊全部在你手中"}]}